name: Ashish-kumar
tagline: “ It's hard enough to find an error in your code when you're looking for it; it's even harder when you've assumed your code is error-free. ”
body: Hey guys! I am Ashish Kumar, a software engineer. I love to program. And I want to update this world into 'DIGITAL WORLD'. Programming is my passion and codes run through my veins.
